Interface ItsNatHttpServlet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatServlet

    public interface ItsNatHttpServlet
extends ItsNatServlet
    Is the ItsNat wrapper of the javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet object. Bridges the normal HTTP servlet infrastructure with ItsNat.
